item.title: CVE-2016-10539|2024-08-06T03:21:52.246Z -- hackerone -- negotiator%20node%20module
item.description: negotiator is an HTTP content negotiator for Node.js and is used by many modules and frameworks including Express and Koa. The header for "Accept-Language", when parsed by negotiator 0.6.0 and earlier is vulnerable to Regular Expression Denial of Service via a specially crafted string.
